Abel Magwitch (“The Convict”) is a fearsome criminal, Magwitch escapes from prison at the beginning ofGreat Expectationsand terrorizes Pip in the cemetery. Pip’s kindness, however, makes a deep impression on him, and he subsequently devotes himself to making a fortune and using it to elevate Pip into a higher social class. Behind the scenes, he becomes Pip’s secret benefactor, funding Pip’s education and opulent lifestyle in London through the lawyer Jaggers.